1
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:58,266
(The All-devouring Whale: Homecoming)

2
00:02:08,466 --> 00:02:09,066
(Episode 5)

3
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:15,566
(Ancestral Hall)

4
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,833
What lecher?

5
00:02:18,233 --> 00:02:19,433
What are they talking about?

6
00:02:22,366 --> 00:02:23,766
To catch the traitor,

7
00:02:24,366 --> 00:02:26,833
I shall not give myself away.

8
00:02:27,333 --> 00:02:27,866
Whatever.

9
00:02:28,666 --> 00:02:30,500
Master, in fact...

10
00:02:31,133 --> 00:02:32,733
I am that lecher.

11
00:02:36,433 --> 00:02:37,533
Oh!

12
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:39,333
I knew you were up to something,

13
00:02:39,533 --> 00:02:41,400
so Yue and I watched you so long outside.

14
00:02:42,033 --> 00:02:42,733
Forget it.

15
00:02:43,333 --> 00:02:44,833
At least I've kept my secret.

16
00:02:46,666 --> 00:02:48,900
Then you must have known about the catfish.

17
00:02:53,266 --> 00:02:55,266
You hid another secret? That's one more crime.

18
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:55,900
All right.

19
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,566
Mister Cheng, just take Mister Liu back to his room.

20
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,966
Move it! Back to your room to reflect on yourself.

21
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,333
Master, were you suggesting

22
00:03:06,833 --> 00:03:09,200
that Mister Liu has something to do with Master Fan?

23
00:03:10,133 --> 00:03:11,533
I thought so before,

24
00:03:12,133 --> 00:03:13,200
but Master Fan

25
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:16,000
shouldn't have any connections with a lecher.

26
00:03:18,433 --> 00:03:19,000
Drop it.

27
00:03:19,966 --> 00:03:20,500
Our priority

28
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:23,266
is the D-class assessment competition

29
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:24,833
that we are going to take.

30
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:29,833
(Ten days later)

31
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:38,600
Wow. It's the first time I have ridden such a mount.

32
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,900
It's kind of adorable.

33
00:03:39,966 --> 00:03:41,000
W... Wait.

34
00:03:48,533 --> 00:03:49,933
Our budgets are tight.

35
00:03:50,366 --> 00:03:52,266
So please make do with it.

36
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:01,566
After so many days of isolated cultivation,

37
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:03,200
it's the competition day finally.

38
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,866
I'm a bit nervous because it's my first time.

39
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:09,000
We are just going to the regional competition venue.

40
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,066
So take it easy.

41
00:04:10,833 --> 00:04:12,200
The plain sects

42
00:04:12,266 --> 00:04:13,800
will gather at their region

43
00:04:14,233 --> 00:04:16,733
and be taken to the competition island by an examiner.

44
00:04:16,833 --> 00:04:19,233
How many plain sects will enter for it in each region?

45
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,433
Three or four in the past.

46
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:22,600
Around a dozen people.

47
00:04:23,066 --> 00:04:24,966
How strong are they? Are they our match?

48
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,033
Who is it?

49
00:04:27,433 --> 00:04:28,666
It's that sheep again.

50
00:04:29,366 --> 00:04:30,666
She is still following us.

51
00:04:32,366 --> 00:04:33,100
A couple of days ago,

52
00:04:33,366 --> 00:04:35,833
I noticed that she kept looking inside from the gate,

53
00:04:36,166 --> 00:04:37,866
but she ran away when I talked to her.

54
00:04:38,133 --> 00:04:39,066
She is so shy.

55
00:04:41,366 --> 00:04:43,366
Look, that's the appointed site ahead.

56
00:04:47,966 --> 00:04:50,966
(Examination Square)

57
00:04:53,433 --> 00:04:55,833
Wh... Why are there so many people here?

58
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:59,100
Well, look at them.

59
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:03,566
Isn't this the big-name B-class sect, the Lingxiao Pavilion?

60
00:05:03,866 --> 00:05:04,900
They still exist?

61
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:07,466
I thought the Lingxiao Pavilion was dissolved already.

62
00:05:07,866 --> 00:05:09,700
Here comes the free bank.

63
00:05:09,833 --> 00:05:11,466
Even a little girl can be their master?

64
00:05:11,533 --> 00:05:13,033
Aren't you short of manpower so much?

65
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,133
Those bastards!

66
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:16,700
Xi.

67
00:05:17,333 --> 00:05:18,100
Ignore them.

68
00:05:28,966 --> 00:05:32,000
(Azurewing Catfon
The League's regional dedicated mount)

69
00:05:32,966 --> 00:05:34,666
It's you. Examiner Li.

70
00:05:35,033 --> 00:05:37,300
Gu Ling, it's been a few years.

71
00:05:38,366 --> 00:05:40,300
(Mister Li, Regioinal Receptionist)
Now you have become the master?

72
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:52,066
(Regional Reception)

73
00:05:52,833 --> 00:05:54,233
Well, examiner Li.

74
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:56,200
Why do so many people take the competition this year?

75
00:05:57,566 --> 00:05:59,466
Because of your Lingxiao Pavilion.

76
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:00,933
Because of us?

77
00:06:01,666 --> 00:06:03,033
Since the Lingxiao Pavilion declined,

78
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,033
its resources were carved up by other sects.

79
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,400
(Attendance Sheet)
Even those plain sects got some,

80
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:09,333
(Wang Xiuling, Kuanglong, Shengnan)
so they have grown up rapidly

81
00:06:09,466 --> 00:06:10,966
and are qualified for the competition.

82
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:15,733
So there are up to eight sects in it this year.

83
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:18,933
Ha-ha. Thanks to you guys.

84
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:22,133
The Lingxiao Pavilion has burnt itself to illuminate us.

85
00:06:22,633 --> 00:06:26,033
Shouldn't we call you the greatest well-doers?

86
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:26,800
You...

87
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:27,433
Quiet.

88
00:06:28,466 --> 00:06:29,666
As you can see,

89
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:30,833
there are eight teams.

90
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:33,633
But the places for the competition island are limited.

91
00:06:34,233 --> 00:06:35,733
As for which shall be filtered out,

92
00:06:36,133 --> 00:06:37,800
it's up to you.

93
00:06:38,300 --> 00:06:40,933
Since your sect gave us many things,

94
00:06:41,166 --> 00:06:43,566
why don't you keep doing good things

95
00:06:44,466 --> 00:06:46,533
and give us the qualification, too?

96
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:49,766
Ha-ha.

97
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:50,900
You...

98
00:06:51,533 --> 00:06:52,266
Be quiet!

99
00:06:54,666 --> 00:06:55,600
Little girl,

100
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:58,300
you've become short-tempered as a master.

101
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,333
You...

102
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:05,666
Tyke, everyone here

103
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:07,400
knows how weak you are.

104
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,566
I suggest you beat it when you still can.

105
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:10,700
Master.

106
00:07:11,266 --> 00:07:12,633
Do you remember which sects of them

107
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,966
robbed us?

108
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:14,866
Certainly.

109
00:07:15,366 --> 00:07:16,533
(The Hongfu Bank)
The Hongfu Bank,

110
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,533
(The Kuangshou Stockade)
the Kuangshou Stockade,

111
00:07:17,833 --> 00:07:18,900
(The Shengnan Sect)
the Shengnan Sect,

112
00:07:19,233 --> 00:07:20,066
(The Yifang Villa)
and the Yifang Villa.

113
00:07:21,366 --> 00:07:22,233
I could never forget them.

114
00:07:22,533 --> 00:07:24,533
Okay. These four sects mentioned,

115
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:26,333
show yourselves now.

116
00:07:27,133 --> 00:07:30,833
We shall show no mercy
since the Lingxiao Pavilion is so arrogant.

117
00:07:31,033 --> 00:07:32,166
Each sect sends a person

118
00:07:32,366 --> 00:07:33,666
to give them a good treatment.

119
00:07:34,766 --> 00:07:36,166
How ignorant they are!

120
00:07:36,466 --> 00:07:38,366
You are underestimating our Hongfu Bank too much.

121
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,900
Wang Fugui.

122
00:07:40,666 --> 00:07:42,233
When Hongfu was robbed,

123
00:07:42,666 --> 00:07:45,033
you survived because of Master Fan's support.

124
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:47,400
Now the Lingxiao Pavilion is in trouble,

125
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:49,366
you don't just return the favor,

126
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,266
but fish in troubled water.

127
00:07:51,533 --> 00:07:52,566
How could you do that?

128
00:07:53,866 --> 00:07:55,900
Stop trying to move us.

129
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,400
Listen up,

130
00:07:57,533 --> 00:07:59,833
the development of sects is so bloody and cruel.

131
00:08:00,166 --> 00:08:02,400
The one who gets more makes the call.

132
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,766
Favor is nothing.

133
00:08:04,266 --> 00:08:07,233
Besides, Fan Lingxiao is dead already.

134
00:08:07,466 --> 00:08:08,566
Very well.

135
00:08:09,533 --> 00:08:10,733
I'm relieved

136
00:08:11,133 --> 00:08:12,533
to hear that.

137
00:08:15,666 --> 00:08:17,166
(Teddy Dog, In the eighth phase of the Soul-building Stage)
It's a spiritual pet in the Soul-building Stage.

138
00:08:17,366 --> 00:08:18,600
They still exist?

139
00:08:18,966 --> 00:08:20,833
I thought the Lingxiao Pavilion was gone.

140
00:08:20,833 --> 00:08:24,200
A mere pet in the Soul-building Stage
makes you so unbridled?

141
00:08:26,333 --> 00:08:27,300
Go get it.

142
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:45,000
You... Come and help.

143
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:48,066
(Red Thorn Pony
In the sixth phase of the Soul-building Stage)

144
00:08:48,466 --> 00:08:50,466
(Rhino Horn Panda
In the fifth phase of the Soul-building Stage)

145
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,600
(Scent Skipper
In the sixth phase of the Soul-building Stage)

146
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,266
You four sects, listen carefully.

147
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,500
You should prepare three times

148
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:02,466
the things you snatched from us.

149
00:09:03,633 --> 00:09:04,566
We will ask you for them

150
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,666
one by one.

151
00:09:07,366 --> 00:09:08,033
Did you hear it?

152
00:09:08,966 --> 00:09:10,366
All right.

153
00:09:10,566 --> 00:09:12,400
We'll return it.

154
00:09:12,966 --> 00:09:16,000
Please spare us. We'll quit the competition.

155
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,800
When you return in triumph,

156
00:09:17,966 --> 00:09:19,733
we will send them to your home.

157
00:09:20,033 --> 00:09:22,433
Please get rid of the poison.

158
00:09:27,466 --> 00:09:28,600
Teddy, detoxify him.

159
00:09:34,466 --> 00:09:35,366
Thank you.

160
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,433
Examiner Li, the problem is solved.

161
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:40,366
Please carry on.

162
00:09:40,666 --> 00:09:41,666
Impressive.

163
00:09:44,633 --> 00:09:45,633
Congratulations, Lingxiao Pavilion.

164
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,433
So the seat for the competition in this region

165
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,400
is decided.

166
00:09:49,866 --> 00:09:50,933
They are the Lingxiao Pavilion,

167
00:09:51,133 --> 00:09:52,033
the Wan'gu Gate,

168
00:09:52,133 --> 00:09:54,066
and the Baimu Study.

169
00:09:55,633 --> 00:09:58,033
Isn't that Gray Hair? You've joined the competition, too?

170
00:09:58,733 --> 00:10:01,133
Rascal, I am Su Muchuan.

171
00:10:01,366 --> 00:10:02,600
Call me Gray Hair again and I'll kill you.

172
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,600
Aren't you a lone trainer?

173
00:10:05,166 --> 00:10:07,233
Huh? For a strong trainer like me,

174
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,566
isn't it quite normal to join a sect?

175
00:10:10,766 --> 00:10:11,200
Hey.

176
00:10:11,766 --> 00:10:13,400
Didn't they just enter the Soul-building Stage last time?

177
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,400
Why are they

178
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,833
in high phases already?

179
00:10:16,666 --> 00:10:17,900
How did you train them?

180
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,866
You have sharp eyes.

181
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:22,500
Had the retired sects been like you,

182
00:10:22,933 --> 00:10:23,966
it would have saved us much effort.

183
00:10:24,733 --> 00:10:25,033
Look,

184
00:10:25,866 --> 00:10:27,366
shall we form an alliance?

185
00:10:29,366 --> 00:10:30,200
That's right.

186
00:10:30,466 --> 00:10:32,866
Why don't the three of our sects ally with each other?

187
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,466
So we can take care of each other.

188
00:10:34,666 --> 00:10:36,033
No. You are too weak.

189
00:10:36,633 --> 00:10:38,733
Your Wangu Gate always catches useless pets.

190
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,300
It's pointless to work with you.

191
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:42,833
You'd better be terminated and go home soon.

192
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,400
You want to die?

193
00:10:45,533 --> 00:10:48,100
Great. Making enemies at once.

194
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,400
Muchuan, quiet.

195
00:10:52,133 --> 00:10:53,366
Yes, Master.

196
00:10:55,333 --> 00:10:57,200
So that is the master of the Baimu Study?

197
00:10:58,133 --> 00:11:00,133
She joins the competition at that age.

198
00:11:00,666 --> 00:11:02,466
It looks like she is pretty strong.

199
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:03,733
Everyone.

200
00:11:04,366 --> 00:11:06,366
The competition will be held on the island soon.

201
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:09,266
Please get on the Catfons.

202
00:11:09,533 --> 00:11:10,866
We are about to leave.

203
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:03,666
Li Jie, here you are at last.

204
00:12:05,733 --> 00:12:09,733
(Consonance
The dedicated spiritual pet for the League's competition)

205
00:12:11,866 --> 00:12:12,866
So cute.

206
00:12:13,933 --> 00:12:16,600
So, how are the candidates of our Fifth Region?

207
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,366
(Lu Wenqing, The examiner of the Fifth Region
Wang Xiao, The examiner of the Fifth Region)

208
00:12:20,566 --> 00:12:21,533
The Lingxiao Pavilion?

209
00:12:22,433 --> 00:12:25,500
Yes. Gu Ling has become its master.

210
00:12:25,766 --> 00:12:26,966
They've arrived in a big way.

211
00:12:27,966 --> 00:12:28,566
Master Gu.

212
00:12:28,766 --> 00:12:30,200
I am a fan of the Lingxiao Pavilion.

213
00:12:30,466 --> 00:12:31,966
I admired Master Fan so much.

214
00:12:32,166 --> 00:12:33,966
The Lingxiao Pavilion rose suddenly as a new force

215
00:12:34,133 --> 00:12:36,033
and defeated many opponents irresistibly.

216
00:12:36,100 --> 00:12:37,466
It was like a legend.

217
00:12:40,633 --> 00:12:41,666
It's a shame that...

218
00:12:42,333 --> 00:12:42,833
This time,

219
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,766
we've come with Master Fan's will

220
00:12:44,966 --> 00:12:47,133
to pick ourselves up. Please guide us.

221
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,600
I have faith in you. Go for it.

222
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:51,700
Thank you, Examiner Lu.

223
00:12:53,366 --> 00:12:55,566
The Lingxiao Pavilion is a favorite to win the competition.

224
00:12:56,133 --> 00:12:57,633
We'd better not irritate them.

225
00:12:58,033 --> 00:12:58,433
All right.

226
00:12:58,966 --> 00:13:01,766
Let me hand out the important items
for the competition to you.

227
00:13:06,633 --> 00:13:08,266
It's a key device in the competition.

228
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:10,800
Please keep the bracelet safe.

229
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,966
And this is...?

230
00:13:12,633 --> 00:13:14,866
It's a new pet breed named Consonance for the competition

231
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:16,133
developed by the League.

232
00:13:16,433 --> 00:13:18,700
When a candidate wears the bracelet
from the pet's head on their wrist,

233
00:13:19,033 --> 00:13:20,800
it may collect real-time data about their behaviors.

234
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:24,300
So the examiners may supervise your conditions.

235
00:13:24,900 --> 00:13:27,066
There are three key rules.

236
00:13:27,266 --> 00:13:28,566
Please keep them in your mind.

237
00:13:29,266 --> 00:13:30,400
To put them simply,

238
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:32,100
first, keep the bracelet on your wrist.

239
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:34,100
Second, the one who falls into the water loses.

240
00:13:34,466 --> 00:13:36,133
Third, the loser is protected.

241
00:13:36,900 --> 00:13:37,900
I understand the first two rules,

242
00:13:38,333 --> 00:13:40,633
but what does the third one mean?

243
00:13:41,166 --> 00:13:43,166
Any attack on the one who yields

244
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:45,466
will terminate all the attackers.

245
00:13:46,233 --> 00:13:48,866
It's made to prevent unnecessary loss of life efficiently.

246
00:13:49,133 --> 00:13:51,933
Now, the competition is about to begin.

247
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:55,366
We are going to take you
to your departure place respectively.

248
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:57,100
The Lingxiao Pavilion stays with me here.

249
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,666
The Baimu Study follows Examiner Li.

250
00:13:59,033 --> 00:14:00,300
The Wan'gu Gate goes with Examiner Wang.

251
00:14:00,966 --> 00:14:03,733
Baimu Study and Wan'gu Gate, this way.

252
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:08,200
That's all the explanation provided.

253
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,800
The competition is about to begin.

254
00:14:10,033 --> 00:14:10,800
I'm leaving this island.

255
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:12,366
By the way,

256
00:14:13,133 --> 00:14:14,433
as a fan of the Lingxiao Pavilion,

257
00:14:14,966 --> 00:14:16,133
this is my personal wish.

258
00:14:16,633 --> 00:14:18,033
I sincerely hope the Pavilion

259
00:14:18,266 --> 00:14:19,300
can make a comeback.

260
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:23,233
Thank you, Examiner Lu.

261
00:14:31,266 --> 00:14:31,666
We're here.

262
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,800
(Command Center)

263
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:41,033
Governor.

264
00:14:41,366 --> 00:14:43,466
The Lingxiao Pavilion, the Wan'gu Gate,
and the Baimu Study are all in position.

265
00:14:44,066 --> 00:14:44,433
(Governor Lv)
Good.

266
00:14:44,433 --> 00:14:45,333
(The commander of the League's competition)

267
00:14:45,366 --> 00:14:46,033
Governor.

268
00:14:46,533 --> 00:14:47,400
Mister Bai has arrived.

269
00:14:48,766 --> 00:14:49,666
At last.

270
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:50,933
I'm sorry, Lord Lv.

271
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:53,466
(Bai Tanshu, The supervisor of the League's competition)
I was delayed on the way.

272
00:14:54,533 --> 00:14:55,700
It's all right, Mister Bai.

273
00:14:55,866 --> 00:14:56,800
You came right on time.

274
00:14:57,300 --> 00:14:59,100
I think I just heard someone
mentioning the Lingxiao Pavilion.

275
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:01,433
They are one of the candidates this year, too?

276
00:15:02,533 --> 00:15:04,100
They entered the B-class before.

277
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,533
Now they are starting over.

278
00:15:05,966 --> 00:15:07,133
Isn't it so miserable?

279
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:08,533
Who is she?

280
00:15:08,666 --> 00:15:10,100
The young lady of the Bais.

281
00:15:10,533 --> 00:15:12,800
Mister Bai is invited as the supervisor this year.

282
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:15,000
It's said he wanted to let his sister see the world,

283
00:15:15,166 --> 00:15:16,133
so he brought her here.

284
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,733
Rumor has it that Master Fan's death

285
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,833
was related to the Bais, is it true?

286
00:15:21,466 --> 00:15:22,200
Just a rumor.

287
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,766
My family would never do such a vile thing.

288
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:27,800
Sorry, Mister Bai.

289
00:15:28,133 --> 00:15:29,133
I just heard about it.

290
00:15:29,166 --> 00:15:30,200
Please don't mind.

291
00:15:31,033 --> 00:15:31,733
I won't.

292
00:15:32,533 --> 00:15:34,333
Since there were two B-class sects in the same prefecture,

293
00:15:34,766 --> 00:15:36,466
it's understandable that people thought

294
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:38,200
we would compete with each other.

295
00:15:39,033 --> 00:15:41,133
I was lucky enough to have a duel with Master Fan.

296
00:15:41,666 --> 00:15:43,233
He was far stronger than me.

297
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:44,800
So I am convinced of my defeat.

298
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:47,066
We were of the same age,

299
00:15:47,466 --> 00:15:49,200
but he could reach such a high realm.

300
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,700
I can only say there is always someone stronger.

301
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:53,933
It's a shame...

302
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,733
Mister Bai.

303
00:15:56,166 --> 00:15:57,366
Everything is ready now.

304
00:15:58,333 --> 00:16:00,833
Please go outside with us
to announce the start of the competition.

305
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,066
Sure, Lord Lv.

306
00:16:02,733 --> 00:16:05,966
(The D-class Assessment Competition)

307
00:16:09,266 --> 00:16:10,266
Listen up.

308
00:16:11,566 --> 00:16:12,866
The D-class assessment competition

309
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,133
begins now.

310
00:16:20,666 --> 00:16:22,366
Look, the level of the water is falling.

311
00:16:22,533 --> 00:16:24,733
No. The whole island is rising.

312
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:26,400
Take it easy, all of you.

313
00:16:26,966 --> 00:16:29,500
The competition island
is generating a complete competition site.

314
00:16:29,966 --> 00:16:30,433
That...

315
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:33,200
That is too dramatic.

316
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,700
All candidates, attention.

317
00:16:39,133 --> 00:16:40,633
The site has been generated.

318
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:42,366
The new areas

319
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:44,266
will be our competition sites.

320
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:45,500
We are...

321
00:16:46,166 --> 00:16:48,200
on the back of a giant turtle!

322
00:16:50,133 --> 00:16:51,166
All examiners.

323
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:53,100
Establish connections with the Consonances.

324
00:17:00,133 --> 00:17:01,633
Let the Bullet Screen launch them.

325
00:17:01,733 --> 00:17:02,100
Yes, sir.

326
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,700
(Bullet Screen
The dedicated spiritual pet for the League's competition)

327
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:09,400
Look at there.

328
00:17:09,600 --> 00:17:12,366
Now I will tell you the score rules.

329
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:15,700
The theme of the first phase is Collecting.

330
00:17:16,233 --> 00:17:19,800
There are 500 beaming score spores at the site.

331
00:17:20,166 --> 00:17:23,733
You'll get one score
if you find one and touch the bracelet with it.

332
00:17:24,366 --> 00:17:26,233
When 300 spores are collected,

333
00:17:26,466 --> 00:17:28,700
the second phase begins.

334
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:31,833
Are those beams given out by the spores?

335
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:33,566
They are so obvious.

336
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,266
Then can't we

337
00:17:36,366 --> 00:17:37,633
see where they are clearly?

338
00:17:38,766 --> 00:17:40,966
Look. There is one close to us.

339
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:45,500
Master, why don't you do it?

340
00:17:48,333 --> 00:17:49,166
It's quite convenient.

341
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,800
There is another one.

342
00:17:51,233 --> 00:17:51,700
I'll go get it.

343
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:53,733
One more score.

344
00:17:55,766 --> 00:17:57,966
That Suslik took our score away.

345
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,633
Is it the spiritual pet of another sect?

346
00:17:59,833 --> 00:18:01,600
Look at the beams far away.

347
00:18:03,166 --> 00:18:04,600
They are reducing rapidly.

348
00:18:05,366 --> 00:18:05,833
What should we do now?

349
00:18:06,133 --> 00:18:07,000
It seems we are too slow.

350
00:18:07,533 --> 00:18:08,833
The spores are almost taken away.

351
00:18:09,166 --> 00:18:10,966
There are 500 spores in the first phase,

352
00:18:11,566 --> 00:18:13,966
and the second phase will start when 300 are collected.

353
00:18:14,733 --> 00:18:16,666
Since we want to rank first,

354
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:18,366
we shall collect more than 20 spores.

355
00:18:19,300 --> 00:18:20,200
We may split up,

356
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:21,866
and each one of us collects five spores at least.

357
00:18:22,633 --> 00:18:24,800
Come to gather here when the first phase is over.

358
00:18:25,466 --> 00:18:26,400
Do keep yourselves safe.

359
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,300
Their scores are increasing quickly.

360
00:18:34,633 --> 00:18:35,633
Eight-teen scores?

361
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:37,633
What

362
00:18:37,966 --> 00:18:39,200
is this Tianyun Sect?

363
00:18:39,633 --> 00:18:41,300
An interesting sect.

364
00:18:41,766 --> 00:18:43,500
They are using the loophole of the rules.

365
00:18:44,633 --> 00:18:46,066
See that red symbol?

366
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,066
They've taken the bracelets off.

367
00:18:53,533 --> 00:18:54,800
I've got one more.

368
00:18:55,033 --> 00:18:55,966
Me, too.

369
00:18:56,366 --> 00:18:58,066
Master is so smart.

370
00:18:58,266 --> 00:18:59,966
Since the bracelets can be taken off for three minutes,

371
00:19:00,333 --> 00:19:02,100
we put them on pets and let them collect spores.

372
00:19:02,366 --> 00:19:03,900
It's efficient and can't be noticed.

373
00:19:04,266 --> 00:19:06,733
We will be far ahead in the first phase.

374
00:19:07,633 --> 00:19:08,433
Where is my pet?

375
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:09,500
I can't sense mine, either.

376
00:19:09,933 --> 00:19:11,233
Are you looking for them?

377
00:19:11,233 --> 00:19:11,833
Who is it?

378
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:17,600
It's not good to play petty tricks.

379
00:19:17,833 --> 00:19:19,966
You rampant idiot! Do you want to die?

380
00:19:20,333 --> 00:19:21,100
Rampant idiot?

381
00:19:23,133 --> 00:19:23,833
Armteeth.

382
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,800
It seems they want to see you.

383
00:19:29,333 --> 00:19:29,766
That...

384
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:35,266
I'm Sheng Liao, from the Beckon Society,

385
00:19:35,566 --> 00:19:36,566
(Sheng Liao, The Beckon Society, a branch of the Ease Sect)
a branch of the Ease Sect.

386
00:19:36,566 --> 00:19:37,433
The Ease Sect?

387
00:19:37,866 --> 00:19:38,633
That is...

388
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:39,966
A parasitic pet.

389
00:19:40,166 --> 00:19:41,400
Without the bracelets,

390
00:19:41,533 --> 00:19:42,866
you can't even yield.

391
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:45,633
You may go to the underworld together.

392
00:19:48,133 --> 00:19:48,633
That is...?

393
00:19:49,133 --> 00:19:50,500
It seems four candidates

394
00:19:50,633 --> 00:19:53,400
failed to put on the bracelets within three minutes.

395
00:19:54,133 --> 00:19:55,366
The Tianyun Sect is terminated.

396
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:57,733
They forgot to put them on after taking the bracelets off.

397
00:19:58,366 --> 00:19:59,166
Their trick failed?

398
00:19:59,533 --> 00:19:59,966
Not exactly.

399
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:01,466
Maybe

400
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,400
they were attacked.

401
00:20:04,366 --> 00:20:05,266
Examiners of the Third Region.

402
00:20:05,666 --> 00:20:07,100
Go to the island to check it out.

403
00:20:07,766 --> 00:20:09,333
Prepare for the worst.

404
00:20:09,333 --> 00:20:09,766
Yes.

405
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,633
All candidates, attention.

406
00:20:11,733 --> 00:20:13,466
The entire Tianyun Sect is terminated.

407
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,700
There are 23 teams left now.

408
00:20:17,666 --> 00:20:18,900
The conflict broke out earlier than I expected.

409
00:20:19,533 --> 00:20:20,600
Guys, be safe.

410
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:26,600
Well done.

411
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:27,533
One more score.

412
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:32,333
Why has that beam disappeared?

413
00:20:33,233 --> 00:20:33,966
We've got company.

414
00:20:34,966 --> 00:20:35,733
Who is there?

415
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,166
This is the Hongluan Building.

416
00:20:37,366 --> 00:20:38,266
Stop hiding.

417
00:20:38,533 --> 00:20:39,666
The Hongluan Building?

418
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:43,066
Isn't it the sect of Xue Dashuai I met before?

419
00:20:43,666 --> 00:20:45,700
- I remember it's a B-class sect. - Show yourself.

420
00:20:46,366 --> 00:20:48,166
- Is it a new branch? - I saw you.

421
00:20:50,166 --> 00:20:51,400
But if I face four people...

422
00:20:51,766 --> 00:20:52,233
Teddy.

423
00:20:57,100 --> 00:20:57,766
Doggy?

424
00:20:57,966 --> 00:20:58,966
Why are you here?

425
00:20:59,933 --> 00:21:01,066
What is going on?

426
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,033
They know each other?

427
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:05,000
Very well. Liu Fengmang.

428
00:21:05,300 --> 00:21:06,000
Come here now!

429
00:21:08,033 --> 00:21:08,966
It's the third one.

430
00:21:09,266 --> 00:21:10,600
Nobody is around. It's safe.

431
00:21:11,533 --> 00:21:12,200
Put it down.

432
00:21:14,633 --> 00:21:15,300
No.

433
00:21:15,366 --> 00:21:17,666
It is a good idea to use the spore as a bait.

434
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,233
Just one person?

435
00:21:20,766 --> 00:21:21,566
It's an ambush.

436
00:21:22,166 --> 00:21:23,366
But there are just two of them.

437
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:25,133
I should be able to handle them.

438
00:21:25,366 --> 00:21:26,066
Little girl.

439
00:21:26,166 --> 00:21:29,366
Tell us your name and sect.

440
00:21:29,666 --> 00:21:30,600
I know her.

441
00:21:31,033 --> 00:21:33,133
She is Gu Ling of the Lingxiao Pavilion.

442
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:35,566
That voice...

443
00:21:38,266 --> 00:21:38,866
Miss Gu.

444
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,233
It's been a while.

445
00:21:41,033 --> 00:21:41,800
Duan Ye?